---
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="INTERGEN | Project"
  description="About the INTERGEN project."
>
  <PageHeader title="About The Project" />

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.7fr_1.3fr]">
      <aside class="lg:sticky lg:top-28 lg:self-start">
        <div class="border border-border bg-muted p-6">
          <p
            class="font-sans text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-primary"
          >
            Project sections
          </p>
          <nav
            class="mt-5 grid gap-3 font-sans text-sm"
            aria-label="Project page sections"
          >
            <a
              class="text-foreground underline hover:text-primary"
              href="#provocation">The provocation behind INTERGEN</a
            >
            <a class="text-foreground underline hover:text-primary" href="#aim"
              >Aim and main tasks</a
            >
            <a
              class="text-foreground underline hover:text-primary"
              href="#outcomes">Outcomes</a
            >
            <a
              class="text-foreground underline hover:text-primary"
              href="#financing">Financing</a
            >
            <a
              class="text-foreground underline hover:text-primary"
              href="#work-packages">Work packages</a
            >
          </nav>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <article
          id="provocation"
          class="scroll-mt-28 border border-border bg-card"
        >
          <div class="border-b border-border px-6 py-5">
            <h2
              class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-foreground"
            >
              The Provocation Behind INTERGEN
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-7 px-6 py-7 leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
            <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8">
              The main purpose of the INTERGEN academic consortium is to support
              different efforts of many people to preserve the family in a
              respectful way, using the following example as a visualization of
              the intergenerational business linkages:
            </p>

            <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
              <section class="border border-border bg-background p-5">
                <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">
                  Example 1
                </h3>
                <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-3 pl-5">
                  <li>The grandparents produce grape</li>
                  <li>
                    The parents produce wine (including the grape of their
                    parents)
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    The children create an on-line shop and they also sell the
                    grape and the wine of their relatives.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </section>

              <section class="border border-border bg-background p-5">
                <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">
                  Example 2
                </h3>
                <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-3 pl-5">
                  <li>The grandparents produce apples</li>
                  <li>
                    The parents produce apple juice (including the fruits of the
                    grandparents)
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    The children create an on-line shop and they also sell the
                    apples and the apple juice of their relatives.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </section>
            </div>

            <div class="border-l-2 border-primary pl-5">
              <p class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">
                Originally described in
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                <a
                  href="http://jei.uni-ruse.bg/Issue-2017/10.%20Pavlov_Sheresheva_Perello.pdf"
                  class="text-foreground underline hover:text-primary"
                >
                  Pavlov, D., Sheresheva, M., Perello, M. (2017). The
                  Intergenerational Small Family Enterprises as Strategic
                  Entities for the Future of the European Civilization - A Point
                  of View // Journal of Entrepreneurship & Innovation, 2017,
                  issue 9, p.p. 26-38, ISSN 1314-0175.
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article id="aim" class="scroll-mt-28 border border-border bg-card">
          <div class="border-b border-border px-6 py-5">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-foreground">
              Aim of the network and main tasks
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-7 px-6 py-7 leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
            <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8">
              To study how the neoclassic concept of the intergenerational
              family businesses could be used as an instrument to manage the
              entrepreneurial stress.
            </p>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">
                The main tasks of the project are:
              </h3>
              <ol
                class="mt-4 divide-y divide-border border border-border bg-background"
              >
                <li class="grid gap-3 px-5 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[3rem_1fr]">
                  <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-primary"
                    >01</span
                  >
                  <span
                    >To study the general attitude of the students for their
                    career development.</span
                  >
                </li>
                <li class="grid gap-3 px-5 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[3rem_1fr]">
                  <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-primary"
                    >02</span
                  >
                  <span
                    >To study the influence of this new concept on their
                    entrepreneurial attitudes.</span
                  >
                </li>
                <li class="grid gap-3 px-5 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[3rem_1fr]">
                  <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-primary"
                    >03</span
                  >
                  <span
                    >To study how this new theory could reduce their
                    entrepreneurial stress.</span
                  >
                </li>
                <li class="grid gap-3 px-5 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[3rem_1fr]">
                  <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-primary"
                    >04</span
                  >
                  <span
                    >To study how this theory could improve their well-being.</span
                  >
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
          <article
            id="outcomes"
            class="scroll-mt-28 border border-border bg-card px-6 py-6"
          >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight text-foreground">
              Outcomes
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
              Improved understanding about the role of the intergenerational
              family businesses for the student development as entrepreneurs.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article
            id="financing"
            class="scroll-mt-28 border border-border bg-card px-6 py-6"
          >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight text-foreground">
              Financing
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
              The project members (especially under HEInnovate concept of the
              European Commission it is expected the research to be done with
              non-public funds, especially from firms).
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <article
          id="work-packages"
          class="scroll-mt-28 border border-border bg-card"
        >
          <div class="border-b border-border px-6 py-5">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-foreground">
              Work packages
            </h2>
          </div>
          <ol class="divide-y divide-border leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
            <li class="grid gap-3 px-6 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr]">
              <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-foreground"
                >WP1</span
              >
              <span>Management.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="grid gap-3 px-6 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr]">
              <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-foreground"
                >WP2</span
              >
              <span>Implementation of a survey among students.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="grid gap-3 px-6 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr]">
              <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-foreground"
                >WP3</span
              >
              <span>Design of publications with the outcomes.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="grid gap-3 px-6 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr]">
              <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-foreground"
                >WP4</span
              >
              <span
                >Dissemination and sustainable exploitation of the results.</span
              >
            </li>
          </ol>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
